      <abstract displayLabel="Abstract">In order for security solutions for application container
                environments to effectively meet their security objectives, it is necessary to
                analyze those security solutions and detail the metrics they must satisfy in the
                form of security assurance requirements. Since Linux and its various distributions
                form the predominant host OS component of the deployed container platforms, the
                focus of this document is on security assurance requirements for security solutions
                for application containers hosted on Linux.</abstract>
